commune with nature
Level-5th
CastingTime-1Minute
Range/Area-Self
School-Divination
Attack/Save-div
OtherInfo-                You briefly become one with nature and gain knowledge of the surrounding territory. In the outdoors, the sell gives you knowledge of the land within 3 miles of you. In caves and other natural underground settings, the radius is limited to 300 feet. The sell doesn't function where nature has been relaced by construction, such as in dungeons and towns.
